OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781553961
OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson has denied that
OL,7,Fhe attended a meeting in the 1990s
OL,8,Fwith an alleged victim to nip her
OL,9,Fclaims of sexual abuse against him "in
OL,10,Fthe bud".
OL,12,FProsecution barrister Rosemary Walsh
OL,13,FKC is continuing to cross-examine the
OL,14,Fformer DUP leader at his historical
OL,15,Fsexual offences trial at Newry Crown
OL,16,FCourt.
OL,18,FDonaldson, 63, has pleaded not guilty
OL,19,Fto 18 alleged offences.
OL,26,@qD@dOUrD@HO]
