OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781553961
OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FResuming her cross-examination on
OL,7,FFriday morning, Ms Walsh referred to a
OL,8,Fphone call Donaldson received in the
OL,9,F1990s from David Hoy, the founder of
OL,10,Fthe Christian Family Centre in Armoy.
OL,12,FThe court has previously heard that
OL,13,FComplainant B stayed at the centre in
OL,14,Fthe 1990s after developing an issue
OL,15,Fwith drugs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
