FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781553961
OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FThe court has also been told that
OL,7,FComplainant B had told a church pastor
OL,8,Fat the centre about the alleged abuse
OL,9,Fand he then introduced her to Mr Hoy
OL,10,Fand his wife and a meeting with
OL,11,FDonaldson was arranged.
OL,13,FThe court has also heard B claim that
OL,14,FDonaldson apologised to her at that
OL,15,Fmeeting.
OL,17,FThe barrister asked Donaldson if he
OL,18,Fdid not see "anything strange" about
OL,19,Fthe approach from Mr Hoy.
OL,26,@zD@MOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
