OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781553961
OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FDonaldson said: "I get lots of phone
OL,7,Fcalls from people I have never met
OL,8,Fbefore in the course of my political
OL,9,Fwork."
OL,11,FMs Walsh suggested that he filtered
OL,12,Fhis phone calls.
OL,14,FHe said: "I don't actually. I have
OL,15,Fgiven my phone number out to many
OL,16,Fpeople over the years."
OL,18,FHe said it was "not unusual" for him
OL,19,Fto get a phone call from someone he
OL,20,Fhad never met before.
OL,26,@nD@QOUqD@FO]vD@JOUxD@WO]zD@POUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
