OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781553961
OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FMs Walsh suggested Donaldson needed to
OL,7,Fmeet Mr Hoy because "he was going to
OL,8,Fbe talking to you about a sensitive
OL,9,Fmatter".
OL,11,FDonaldson said: "That is absolutely
OL,12,Fnot true."
OL,14,FHe said he had not tried to "avoid the
OL,15,Fmeeting", and was happy to meet Mr Hoy.
OL,17,FMs Walsh said: "You had to go on the
OL,18,Fdefensive to deal with this?"
OL,20,FDonaldson said: "That is not true."
OL,26,@oD@UOUqD@GO]sD@QOUtD@JO]vD@]OUwD@HO]yD@
OL,26,APOUzD@]O]|D@QOU|D@cO]
