OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FMs Walsh asked if Mr Hoy had "made up"
OL,7,Fthe evidence that an allegation had
OL,8,Fbeen made.
OL,10,FHe said: "I am saying he is mistaken
OL,11,Fin his recollection."
OL,13,FMs Walsh said Donaldson had attended
OL,14,Fthe meeting in Armoy as he "knew this
OL,15,Fwas something you needed to nip in the
OL,16,Fbud".
OL,18,FHe said: "That is not true at all."
