OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FMs Walsh pointed out that before the
OL,7,Fmeeting Complainant B had first raised
OL,8,Fthe allegations against Donaldson with
OL,9,Fsomeone else.
OL,11,FHe said: "I had no knowledge
OL,12,Fwhatsoever of any of that."
OL,14,FMs Walsh asked the former MP if the
OL,15,Fmeeting had involved him apologising.
OL,17,FDonaldson said he had said he was
OL,18,F"sorry if she felt uncomfortable".
OL,20,FThe barrister asked: "What were you
OL,21,Fapologising for?"
OL,26,@sD@JOUtD@[O]zD@AOUzD@aO]|D@VOU}D@QO]
