OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FHe said: "That she felt uncomfortable."
OL,8,FMs Walsh suggested he was "trying to
OL,9,Ffind a reason why you apologised to
OL,10,Fher".
OL,12,FHe said: "Not at all."
OL,14,FHe added: "I went to Armoy in good
OL,15,Ffaith and I have faithfully relayed to
OL,16,Fyou what the meeting was about."
OL,18,FMs Walsh suggested Donaldson had
OL,19,F"taken control" of the meeting.
OL,21,FHe said: "No, not at all."
