OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FShe said: "You went in there and said
OL,7,Fyou knew what all this was about and
OL,8,Fyou were truly sorry."
OL,10,FHe said: "That is absolutely to
OL,11,Fmisrepresent what happened at that
OL,12,Fmeeting, that is not the case at all."
OL,14,FMs Walsh suggested Donaldson did not
OL,15,Fwant Complainant B "going through
OL,16,Fallegations".
OL,18,FHe said: "That is absolutely not true."
OL,20,FShe said: "You shut her down?"
