OL,3,CDonaldson denies meeting alleged
OL,4,Cvictim to nip claims 'in the bud'
OL,6,FHe said: "No."
OL,8,FMs Walsh said: "When she did recoil,
OL,9,Fyou laughed it off?"
OL,11,FHe said: "No."
OL,13,FThe barrister asked: "She is lying
OL,14,Fabout that?"
OL,16,FHe said: "Yes."
